data.description:
ASSUMABLE VA LOAN with a 2.5% interest rate! Call for more information!

Beautiful, brick Tudor home built in 1908. There is history all throughout, including 8 fireplaces, original pocket doors and so much more. On both floors, you'll find beautiful original hardwood floors and 12 foot ceilings. There are plenty of seating areas that include the living room, sunroom and private covered back deck. Very well maintained. 2 car carport and 1 car garage. The unfinished basement offers plenty of storage. What a great place to call home. 

Roof is approximately 3 years old.
